        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Black Lung Benefits Disability Trust Fund Solvency Act</strong></p> <p>This bill extends until December 31, 2029, the excise tax on coal from U.S. mines. The tax is a source of funding for the&nbsp;Black Lung Disability Trust Fund.</p>]]></text>
